All players choosing Javier will receive additional ability: Ability_Tower_Lock. 

Ability_Tower_Lock: You need 3 tokens instead of 1 token to unlock your NE Area for one stage. If you're the phantom you need 
5 token each to be able to capture your towers there. (rule)

Proposal from Rush_FTK(will be applied in the next game)
Ability_Tower_Lock: Ability_Tower_Lock: You need to spend 3/8/13/18 tokens for the permission to capture your 1/2/3/4 towers. 
Without permission your capturing infantry will simply be attacked. Any tower out of the vision of the mod is regarded as a tower 
captured by you. (rule)
